The total budget allocated for the project is 3 million euros over a duration of 4 years. While detailed cost breakdowns are not provided due to the absence of specific information, our approach focuses on optimizing costs through efficient resource allocation, renegotiation with subcontractors if necessary, and ensuring that annual operational costs remain within the City's budgetary capacities.

### 6. Conclusion
Nexus Engineering S.r.l. and its consortium partners are confident in their ability to deliver a comprehensive AI solution that meets the City of Belval's requirements for enhancing administrative efficiency, quality of service, and regulatory compliance while minimizing environmental impact. Through our commitment to innovation, sustainability, and customer satisfaction, we look forward to collaborating with the City of Belval on this strategic project.
